      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver or a great project car for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor dings, and fading clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it remains functional and has been regularly serviced, though it may soon require attention to some suspension components and tires. It's an honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation.",
