      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for functional transportation. While the engine and transmission are operational and the car remains reliable for commuting, it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scuffs, some fading paint on the hood and roof, and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear, and the air conditioning takes a few minutes to get cold. This is an honest, high-mileage vehicle that has been maintained to keep it running, but it is not in showroom condition.",
