    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant with its signature individual throttle bodies. The dual-VANOS system has been professionally serviced to ensure precise variable valve timing, while the rear subframe\u2014a known structural point\u2014has been reinforced for long-term chassis integrity. Power is managed via a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential, providing exceptional traction out of corners. The suspension retains its factory-tuned kinematics, offering a communicative steering rack and composed damping. A mechanically robust specimen ready for spirited canyon runs or track day duty.",
